If you were under the impression that red wine can’t play nice with poultry, the juicy Good Natured Organic Shiraz 2021 will make you reconsider. With intense mulberry and sweet spice leading to a soft, smooth finish, this certified organic Shiraz is the perfect partner to this Greek-inspired chicken salad – crammed with roasted vegetables, feta, and olives. The recipe, compliments of Spier, serves four. 